@startuml sequence-committee-review
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Assistance Request -- Committee Review & Voting Sequence

actor "Committee\nMember" as CM
participant "Review Dashboard UI" as UI
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "CommitteeReviewService" as CRS
participant "VotingService" as VS
participant "Document Vault\n(Storage)" as DV
participant "Notification Service" as NS
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Reviewer Assignment (Automated) ==

[-> CRS : OnRequestSubmitted event
CRS -> DB : Fetch active committee members
DB --> CRS : Committee roster

CRS -> CRS : Exclude members from\nsame community group\n(conflict of interest)

CRS -> CRS : Select 5 reviewers\n(round-robin / least-loaded)

loop For each of 5 selected reviewers
    CRS -> DB : INSERT ReviewAssignment\n{ requestId, committeeMemberId,\ndeadline = now()+48h }
    DB --> CRS : Saved
    CRS -> NS : Notify committee member\n"New review assigned"
end

CRS -> DB : UPDATE AssistanceRequest\nSET Status = UnderReview,\nReviewStartedAt = now()
DB --> CRS : Updated

CRS -> NS : Notify member\n"Your request is under review"

== Committee Member Reviews Request ==

CM -> UI : Open Review Dashboard
UI -> API : GET /api/v1/committee/reviews/pending
API -> CRS : GetPendingReviews(committeeMemberId)
CRS -> DB : Fetch assigned reviews\nwhere voted = false
DB --> CRS : List of assignments
CRS --> API : ReviewAssignment[]
API --> UI : Display pending reviews

CM -> UI : Select a request to review
UI -> API : GET /api/v1/committee/reviews/{requestId}
API -> CRS : GetReviewDetail(requestId)
CRS -> DB : Fetch request + member standing\n(anonymized member ID)
DB --> CRS : Request detail
CRS --> API : Request detail DTO
API --> UI : Show request detail

CM -> UI : View uploaded documents
UI -> API : GET /api/v1/documents/{storageKey}
API -> DV : Generate pre-signed URL\n(1-hour expiry)
DV --> API : Signed URL
API --> UI : Document viewer

== Voting ==

CM -> UI : Vote "Approve" or "Deny"\nwith justification
UI -> API : POST /api/v1/committee/reviews/{assignmentId}/vote\n{ outcome, justification }
API -> VS : CastVote(assignmentId, dto)

VS -> DB : Verify assignment belongs to\ncommittee member and not expired
DB --> VS : Valid

VS -> DB : INSERT CommitteeVote\n{ outcome, justification, votedAt }
DB --> VS : Saved

VS -> VS : HasQuorum(requestId)
VS -> DB : Count votes for request
DB --> VS : voteCount

alt quorum not yet reached (< 3 of 5)
    VS --> API : 200 OK "Vote recorded"
    API --> UI : "Vote recorded. Awaiting other reviewers."
else quorum reached (>= 3 votes)
    VS -> VS : TallyVotes(requestId)
    VS -> DB : Fetch all votes
    DB --> VS : votes[]

    VS -> VS : Majority determines outcome\n(3+ Approve = Approved,\n3+ Deny = Denied)

    alt Majority = Approve
        VS -> CRS : FinalizeDecision(requestId)
        CRS -> DB : UPDATE AssistanceRequest\nSET Status = Approved,\nApprovedAmount = requestedAmount,\nDecisionAt = now()
        DB --> CRS : Updated
        CRS -> NS : Notify member\n"Your request has been approved!\nEstimated payout: 48-72 hours"
        note right : Triggers Payout Processing\n(L1-4)
    else Majority = Deny
        VS -> CRS : FinalizeDecision(requestId)
        CRS -> DB : UPDATE AssistanceRequest\nSET Status = Denied,\nDenialReason = category-level reason,\nDecisionAt = now()
        DB --> CRS : Updated
        CRS -> NS : Notify member\n"Your request was not approved.\nYou may appeal within 14 days."
    end

    VS --> API : 200 OK "Decision finalized"
    API --> UI : "Decision recorded."
end

== Voting Deadline Expiry (Background Job) ==

[-> CRS : Scheduled check every hour
CRS -> DB : Fetch assignments past deadline\nwithout vote
DB --> CRS : Expired assignments

loop For each expired assignment
    CRS -> DB : Mark assignment as expired
    CRS -> NS : Notify committee member\n"Review deadline missed"
end

CRS -> CRS : If remaining votes sufficient\nfor quorum, continue.\nElse assign replacement reviewer.

@enduml
